name: Friends-with-parse
tagline: Starter project for setting up a friend relation (including request) with Parse.com and Swift
body:
### Welcome to Friends With Parse
Friends with Parse is Swift start project, implementing sending and receiving Friend Requests, as well as displaying a friend list. All necessary Parse Querys is included. All you need is to add your Parse keys and set up your application Classes accordingly.
